      <title>沃伦·巴菲特的粉丝为他离开后制定了自己的路线</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/warren-buffetts-fans-plot-their-own-course-when-he-leaves-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[93岁的伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司首席执行官、亿万富翁沃伦·巴菲特在思考自己的未来时，周六告诉股东，如果幸运的话，他还能再活六七年，但他补充说，“这可能明天就结束了”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/warren-buffetts-fans-plot-their-own-course-when-he-leaves-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 10:02:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
